Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.37,0:00:06.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.74,0:00:08.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.00,0:00:17.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.09,0:00:26.49,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.51,0:00:30.08,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.10,0:00:35.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between the sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.65,0:00:41.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.78,0:00:48.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good time just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.58,0:00:53.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.04,0:00:55.32,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.34,0:01:03.34,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.43,0:01:12.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.85,0:01:16.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.40,0:01:21.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.99,0:01:28.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing, \Nlet's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.12,0:01:34.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave the rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.87,0:01:39.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.42,0:01:41.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.67,0:01:45.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.01,0:01:49.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.06,0:01:50.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.68,0:01:52.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.39,0:01:54.08,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.10,0:01:55.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.73,0:01:57.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.40,0:01:59.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.07,0:02:00.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.44,0:02:01.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.53,0:02:05.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.91,0:02:08.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:12.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.54,0:02:14.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.71,0:02:19.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.09,0:02:21.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.42,0:02:25.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.76,0:02:32.82,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.84,0:02:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.13,0:02:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.93,0:02:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.97,0:02:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.31,0:02:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.27,0:02:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.36,0:03:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.45,0:03:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered \Na Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.45,0:03:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it a quiet night?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.32,0:03:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on watch, but it's \Nbeen calm all night long.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.03,0:03:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no need to man the helm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.66,0:03:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm working myself to the bone for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.32,0:03:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that I'm all bones!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.67,0:03:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.84,0:03:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laboon...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.91,0:03:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know Luffy-san and his buddies?\NI've joined their crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.45,0:03:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are great people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.06,0:03:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they are more than just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.12,0:04:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found something incredible\Nearlier this afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.87,0:04:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It told of Luffy-san and his crew's fearsome\Nadventures and their battle-filled days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.57,0:04:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I have joined them,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.48,0:04:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must prove that I am worthy\Nto call myself a crewmate!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.08,0:04:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't you agree, Laboon?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.62,0:04:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.99,0:04:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wake you up with a song.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.06,0:04:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--♪ White handkerchief, ♪\N--Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.23,0:04:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--♪ don't let him find you ♪\N--The sun hasn't risen yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.96,0:04:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--♪ Run for it ♪\N--Let me catch some more Z's!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.60,0:04:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--♪ White handkerchief... ♪\N--Forget Brook. Someone make\NLuffy stop snoring!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.44,0:04:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Brook's Great Struggle! Is the Path\Nto Becoming a True Comrade Rigorous?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.51,0:04:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the plan, Navigator?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.95,0:04:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we use the paddle, we could keep\Nmoving through these calm waters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.39,0:05:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Based on the weather,\Nthis lull should only last today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.19,0:05:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we don't need to use our precious cola.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.36,0:05:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is good!\NSanji, your cooking really is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.69,0:05:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-chan, have a second\Nhelping of the seafood salad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.11,0:05:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.91,0:05:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's gotten into you, Brook?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.54,0:05:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why have you been so hyper all morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.91,0:05:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something exciting happen, Brook?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.32,0:05:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said that he saw our ship's log\Nwhile he was on watch yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.09,0:05:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! I just so happened\Nto read a small portion of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.59,0:05:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, it left me astonished!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.13,0:05:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been able to \Nsettle down ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.63,0:05:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The incident at Thriller Bark was\Nonly the tip of the iceberg for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.63,0:05:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stopped a civil war in\Nthe desert kingdom, Alabasta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You had a grand adventure\Non the legendary sky island!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.47,0:05:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, you took on \Nthe World Government in a
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.19,0:05:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,massive fight at Water Seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.01,0:05:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so surprised, I \Nnearly had a heart attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.52,0:06:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but I don't have a heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.29,0:06:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I wonder what sort of stories\Nwill get added to the log.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.66,0:06:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brook, your name is going to\Nstart appearing in it now, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.53,0:06:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About that! Now that I am your crewmate,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it is imperative that I make myself useful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.44,0:06:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get why you're eager to work hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.33,0:06:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nbut first let me give you a word of advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.54,0:06:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to hear it, Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.08,0:06:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this crew, never let your\Nguard down during a meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.18,0:06:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it! I, Quick Draw Brook, shall be
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.58,0:06:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nready for the enemy to strike at any time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.92,0:06:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently we didn't warn you soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I claim those noodles!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.19,0:06:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please wait a second! Luffy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.10,0:06:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.27,0:06:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should not have let my guard down,\Neven for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.52,0:06:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well! I shall work \Nmyself to the bone to become
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.86,0:06:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a true pal as soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.98,0:07:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm already nothing but bones...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.08,0:07:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.70,0:07:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate it. Since \Nyou're washing the dishes,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.89,0:07:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can take my time with Nami-san's tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.82,0:07:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As your pal, I am dying to help\Neveryone in extravagant ways,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.23,0:07:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'll do anything to make\Nmyself useful for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.60,0:07:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a great attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.40,0:07:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I'm a skeleton, I should work\Ntill I'm bone tired on the small stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.57,0:07:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm going to give Nami-san her tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.28,0:07:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Sanji-san, where do these go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.71,0:07:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, over in the...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't drop them, even if it kills you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm already dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.52,0:07:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--And "kaboom!"\N--Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.26,0:07:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.73,0:07:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Splendid!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.60,0:07:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.34,0:08:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't trust you to do the dishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.23,0:08:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, then I'll take this \Ntea to Nami-san instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Wait! I was gonna take it to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.42,0:08:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san, I've brought you some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.12,0:08:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.89,0:08:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I see your panties?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.96,0:08:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Bam!\N--That came out of nowhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.56,0:08:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a nautical chart?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.26,0:08:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been pretty busy lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.90,0:08:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a great chance to work on it,\Nsince the ship isn't going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.96,0:08:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it your dream to \Ndraw a map of the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.94,0:08:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. I want to navigate\Nacross the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.01,0:08:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and make a world map based on what I've seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.51,0:08:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.80,0:08:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there is anything\NI could do to help, please let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.56,0:08:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, would you like another cup?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.76,0:08:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.16,0:08:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sentiment is enough for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.38,0:09:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are both beautiful and humble!\NNami-san, you truly are wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.17,0:09:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really! I'm not that great.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.27,0:09:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you truly are--ouch! Hot! Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.97,0:09:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.47,0:09:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, I nearly burned my fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I have any skin to burn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.22,0:09:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My map!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.22,0:09:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What have I done?!\NThat was horribly careless of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.22,0:09:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.79,0:09:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! I wiped it clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.92,0:09:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you wiped it clean of everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.56,0:09:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.80,0:09:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be taking my leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.93,0:09:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get the feeling that I won't be\Nthe least bit useful if this keeps up...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.37,0:09:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.97,0:09:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.41,0:09:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These two are about to do something neat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.85,0:09:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.78,0:09:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.42,0:09:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper-san, what are you doing up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.39,0:09:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm drying these herbs in the sun,\Nsince the weather is so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.96,0:10:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, Franky is gonna test his new weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.86,0:10:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! This is the long-distance\N"Super Franky Cannon."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.80,0:10:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It runs on cola energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.57,0:10:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its range is several times
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.14,0:10:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that of a conventional cannon. \NPlus it's super accurate!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.77,0:10:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Combined with my sniper skills,\Nwe'll be totally unstoppable!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.38,0:10:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.18,0:10:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have butterflies in my stomach!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.78,0:10:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.22,0:10:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me! Let me know if there\Nis anything I could do to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.69,0:10:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. In that case, please get\Nanother barrel of cola to play it safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.26,0:10:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a problem. It would be my pleasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.36,0:10:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.27,0:10:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the barrel of cola!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.94,0:10:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great! Now if you could pour it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.51,0:10:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.79,0:10:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Target: That rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.74,0:10:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it! Locking on to the rock at 2 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.81,0:11:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Fire!\N--Firing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.75,0:11:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh?\N--That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.59,0:11:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp, increase the pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.36,0:11:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, you've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.86,0:11:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, this doesn't look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.28,0:11:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was a huge flop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.95,0:11:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It should have worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.72,0:11:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is kinda salty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.06,0:11:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something is mixed with the cola.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.45,0:11:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is soy sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.49,0:11:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.93,0:11:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show a little remorse!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.43,0:11:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mistook a soy sauce barrel\Nfor a cola barrel, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.47,0:11:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're right! This \Nwas a soy sauce barrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.30,0:11:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannon believe I made that mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.74,0:11:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.08,0:11:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm terribly sorry!\N--Why did you grab a soy sauce barrel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.98,0:12:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm sorry!\N--This is no time for puns!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.98,0:12:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brook, you're hilarious!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.92,0:12:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Don't give me any "I'm only bones" crap!\N--Now I'm all sticky!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.75,0:12:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, I have to wash all of\Nthe herbs I had set out to dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.75,0:12:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This meat tastes great\Nwith the soy sauce and cola!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.86,0:12:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you find a bright side to anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.53,0:12:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything I try ends up going horribly awry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.80,0:12:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, Zoro-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.31,0:12:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to watch in admiration!\NI'm a fellow swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.29,0:12:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this meditation?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.72,0:12:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You enter a state of nothingness\Nwhile making your mind and body one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.03,0:12:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall join you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.21,0:12:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, Zoro-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.03,0:13:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am fully aware that it is improper to\Ntalk during meditation sessions, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.71,0:13:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.44,0:13:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Well, you see...\N--What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.75,0:13:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to use the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.51,0:13:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't need to know that! Head on over--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.98,0:13:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--The thing is...\N--What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.52,0:13:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...my legs went numb, so I can't stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.75,0:13:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any muscles to go numb?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.79,0:13:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro-san, I'm on the verge\Nof having an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.54,0:13:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For real? W-Wait, hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.49,0:13:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm gonna leak! It's coming!\N--I'll take you! W-Wait! Hey, hold it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.83,0:13:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite what I want, I've \Nbeen nothing but a nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.51,0:13:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.94,0:13:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.37,0:13:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.61,0:13:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything I could \Ndo to be of assistance?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.58,0:13:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.82,0:13:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.98,0:13:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brook, why are you so anxious?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.19,0:13:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anxious?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.62,0:13:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get the feeling you're afraid\Nof something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.94,0:13:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I mistaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.16,0:14:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are absolutely right, Robin-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.20,0:14:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I am terribly \Nanxious and scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.27,0:14:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Luffy-san first asked me\Nto join his crew, I was thrilled!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.98,0:14:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those simple words filled me with joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.41,0:14:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then my heart danced
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.59,0:14:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with excitement when I defeated \NOars alongside everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.59,0:14:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I join your crew?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.06,0:14:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.23,0:14:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.23,0:14:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But does he truly want me in his crew?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.33,0:14:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we continue to head toward the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.37,0:14:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no doubt that powerful foes and\Ntrials beyond our imagination await us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.80,0:14:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid that I will be\Nboth useless and a hindrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.21,0:14:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if that proves true, I
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.35,0:14:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,might get kicked off the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.04,0:14:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... I'm afraid\Nof losing my friends again
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.56,0:15:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and returning to that\Npainfully long life of solitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.39,0:15:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.26,0:15:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...also anxious for the longest of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.14,0:15:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.68,0:15:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...also anxious for the longest of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.02,0:15:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was constantly afraid that I\Nwas unworthy to be their friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.95,0:15:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why I believed I could\Nbecome worthy of them
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.02,0:15:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by throwing away my life for their sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.35,0:15:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.10,0:15:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how far I go on the sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.91,0:15:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a huge enemy that I can't shake off...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.28,0:15:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...because the world and\Nits darkness are my enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.62,0:16:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I didn't want\Nyou to come to rescue me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.81,0:16:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm going to die someday anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.72,0:16:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to die right here, right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.36,0:16:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't realize that was how you felt...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.30,0:16:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.07,0:16:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't what it means to be a true friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.82,0:16:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.13,0:16:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.96,0:16:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oomph!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.98,0:16:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brook, we've got food! It's lunchtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.35,0:16:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.35,0:16:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji worked extra hard to make\Na full-course seafood lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.12,0:16:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just know it'll be good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.09,0:16:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.85,0:16:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's keeping you? Get a move on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.53,0:16:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you absolutely certain I'm welcome?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.48,0:16:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NThat I may join the Straw Hat Crew?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.43,0:16:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.77,0:16:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, give it some thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.70,0:17:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided to let you join,\Nso I'm glad to have you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.91,0:17:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now forget about that. Let's eat! Food!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.31,0:17:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.15,0:18:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the Straw Hats have \Ncalm days like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.40,0:18:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp, let's catch dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.31,0:18:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.20,0:18:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many years--no, decades--has it been
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.91,0:18:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nsince I enjoyed such a carefree nap?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.46,0:18:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Brook! Are you gonna sleep forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.70,0:18:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up! We spotted an island!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.76,0:18:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a summer island! It has a beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.29,0:18:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was wandering the ocean alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.86,0:19:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would dream about my old\Nfriends and Laboon in my sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.54,0:19:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would jump awake with happiness,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.31,0:19:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,only to face the painful reality\Nfilled with despair and solitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.44,0:19:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sleep was by no means a peaceful escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.89,0:19:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I listen carefully now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.70,0:19:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Robin, what do you \Nthink of these outfits?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.21,0:19:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I think you'd look \Ngood in this and this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.58,0:19:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.62,0:20:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.19,0:20:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My pals are near me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.73,0:20:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even dead and skeletonized...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.70,0:20:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm truly glad to be alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.47,0:22:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a short break time
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.57,0:22:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before the next adventure \Neventually falls upon us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.00,0:22:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, let your weary bones rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.73,0:22:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laboon,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.29,0:22:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it looks like I will have
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.45,0:22:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a slew of stories to \Nshare when we meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.79,0:22:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you're looking forward to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.94,0:22:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wind has picked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.32,0:22:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.23,0:22:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.29,0:22:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oomph!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.36,0:22:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about time we set out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.23,0:22:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.83,0:23:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise to work my butt off!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.27,0:23:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm a skeleton, so I don't have a butt.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.55,0:23:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've reached the Red Line at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.42,0:23:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll finally get to see Fishman Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.78,0:23:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are the mermaids?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.43,0:23:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see any mermaids,\Nbut there is a sea monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.02,0:23:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.95,0:23:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something popped out\Nwhen I whacked its stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.03,0:23:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could that be a--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.73,0:23:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.26,0:23:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Halfway Across the Grand Line!\NArrival at the Red Line!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.23,0:23:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
